### Stop an app

```
Example Request
```

```shell
curl "https://api.example.org/v3/apps/[guid]/actions/stop" \
  -X POST \
  -H "Authorization: bearer [token]"
```

```
Example Response
```

```http
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json

<%= yield_content :app_with_state, 'STOPPED' %>
```

#### Definition
`POST /v3/apps/:guid/actions/stop`

